episodes.title: 2001 French documentary into Guru Maharaji (Prem Rawat)
episodes.description:
Peace at a price. The money trail. From videos and events to Prem Rawat's pocket. 
http://mikefinch.com/mj/art.htm
Breaking up families, making money from vulnerable devotees who have been brainwashed to believe he is a god. He sets up charities to provide cover for his operations in the same way Jimmy Savile, Sathya Sai Baba and other conmen do. 
Hires conference halls in UN buildings and prestigious universities to give the false impression that these establishments support him.
